<ab facs="#facs_252_r1l6"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> / Doch dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>R<ex>ömıſchen</ex></expan> etc kunıg ʒu </ab>
