<ab>Der stat czu Myze </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns ist <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.
                        künigs brief einr <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>
<expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>, darinn uns sein
                            <expan>künigl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade schreibt und begert,
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> mit zweyen zentnern püchsenpulfers
                        hilfflich zusein; und wie wol wir sölichs <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
                        zewges selb notdurftig <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>, doch dem
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem <expan>r<ex>ömischen</ex></expan> etc.
                        kunig zu dienst und <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu lieb <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> zwen <expan>zentn<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>pulf<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, ob ir der <expan>bedurffe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        werdt, <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>, wem ir die von
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> bey uns befelht zu
                            <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und <expan>einczuneme<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        wan wir die niht wol getrawten selb weg <expan>zu fertig<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        von unpewung der strassen. Und wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
